{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2b01e4363e","title":"中共清华大学委员会关于黄万里同志右派问题的改正决定","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"792be8c008","index":0,"year":1980,"month":2,"day":26,"articleId":"2b01e4363e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"86b82bb2e9","name":"(黄万里)"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4617011f77","type":"title","text":"中共清华大学委员会关于黄万里同志右派问题的改正决定","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2b01e4363e"},{"id":"4506d97d71","type":"authors","text":"(黄万里)","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2b01e4363e"},{"id":"0a74935757","type":"paragraph","text":"黄万里同志，于1958年3月被定为右派分子，1978年2月摘掉右派分子帽子，现任水利系泥沙研究室教授。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2b01e4363e"},{"id":"d4b52e638b","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央(1978)55号文件的精神，我们对黄万里同志的原划右派问题进行了复查，按照1957年中共中央关于《划分右派分子的标准》的规定，黄万里同志原划右派问题属于错划，经中共北京市委批准予以改正，恢复政治名誉，恢复高教二级教授的工资待遇。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2b01e4363e"},{"id":"6fcc9e6cb6","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共清华大学委员会清华大学1980年2月26日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2b01e4363e"}],"page":{"id":"c324f01550","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2b01e4363e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}